title: What should we expect from Auburn's defense down the stretch? Beat writers discuss
text:
After another rough outing in SEC play, what should fans expect from Auburn's defense in the final five games of the regular season?
Top defensive end Carl Lawson is expected to return , but how much of a difference can he make?
AL.com beat writers Brandon Marcello, James Crepea and Wesley Sinor share their thoughts in the video above.
